HTTP Methods

Postman:

CRUD:
created/read/update/delete

Get: 
Retrieve information from server
Encodeed in url

Post:(create)
careat and /or update/replace

http://localhost:9000/ip (get)
give all ip addresses

http://localhost:9000/ip/<xyz> (get)
information about just this particular ip address

http://localhost:9000/ip (post)
create a new ip address info, contents will be in the post body

http://localhost:9000/ip/<xyz> (get)
get xyz

http://localhost:9000/ip/<xyz>  (delete)
delete xyz

http://localhost:9000/ip/<xyz>  (put)
update xyz

http://localhost:9000/ip/<xyz>  (post)
update/replace: xyz

Put:
update only select fields

Rest over HTTP

Delete:
delete